data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED and has done a price improvement AND is offering $5,000 towards Buyer’s closing cost on this CANAL FRONT 4/2 block home with nearly 2,000SqFt is waiting for its new owner. All recently renovated just for you, NEW A/C, NEW Flooring, fixtures, bathrooms, paint, sliding barn closet doors etc. So fresh and so clean for you to set up how you'd like it. There is bonus space off the back room and off of the living room you could make an office. Here is a video walk through of the home and property that you can watch now: https://vimeo.com/842932033 The water views you get looking out back are so beautiful. You'll love the option of fishing in your own backyard or jumping in your boat and going out to the 419 acre lake - Pine Island Lake to fish or just float around. Although the garage has just a single door it is almost 400SqFt giving you a HUGE area to store your ATV/UTV, set up a workshop or storage. Roof was installed in 2016. Conveniently located just 4.5 miles to charming downtown Groveland and Lake David where you can often find events to attend. Groveland has grocery, general shopping, restaurants and more. Walt Disney World®, MCO, Top Medical Facilities and anything you could possibly need are all minutes or less than an hour away. Being right in Central Florida offers the luxury of being on either coast lines in just over an hour. This property is what everyone is looking for so book your showing today.
